description: Heinz Ketchup is great on your burgers, fries and anything else you can think of! More Canadians prefer Heinz ketchup over any other competitor. Today, Heinz Tomato Ketchup is still made with fresh red, ripe and juicy Heinz tomatoes, carefully blended with our unique spices to give you the signature thick and rich taste. Ingredients: TOMATO PASTE (FROM FRESH RIPE TOMATOES), LIQUID SUGAR, VINEGAR, SALT, ONION POWDER, SPICES.
